title: Enhancify
body: Enhance your Spotify experience with a real time listening analysis. View your top songs and artists and discover new music you'll love.

title: Car-Bon
body: Automatically track your car's carbon footprint. Learn about the effects of passenger vehicle carbon emissions and ways to help reduce your footprint.

title: Fuelr
body: Save both money and time by pre-planning the most optimal gas stops for your road trip. Calculated using each gas station's current price and rating.

title: UShoe
body: Receive notifications for new releases of shoes you may like from an AI model trained on images of your favorite shoes.

title: Anti-Troll Discord Bot
body: Prevent trolling in your personal discord server with the added benefit of server and user specific insights.
